title: The Offensive Powerhouses Keep Rolling in the Divisional Round | The Ringer NFL Show (Ep. 383)
description:
The conference championships are set. The Saints edged out the Eagles (6:30), the Patriots pasted the Chargers (17:00), the Rams handled the Cowboys (26:30), and the Chiefs outshined the Colts (33:30).
Hosts: Robert Mays and Kevin Clark
